      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6 faq-items">
        <details class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 group cursor-pointer marker:content-[''] border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-[#00a3e0] transition-all overflow-hidden bg-white/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          <summary class="text-xl font-bold text-[#004b87] flex justify-between items-center outline-none list-none marker:content-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            ¿Cuándo debo acudir a un especialista médico?
            <i class="ph ph-caret-down transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-[#00a3e0] text-2xl"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 pr-8">
            Debes acudir a un especialista cuando presentas síntomas persistentes, dolor continuo o cuando necesitas un diagnóstico más preciso en áreas como cardiología, neurología o gastroenterología.
          </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 group cursor-pointer marker:content-[''] border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-[#00a3e0] transition-all overflow-hidden bg-white/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          <summary class="text-xl font-bold text-[#004b87] flex justify-between items-center outline-none list-none marker:content-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            ¿Qué hace un médico especialista?
            <i class="ph ph-caret-down transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-[#00a3e0] text-2xl"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 pr-8">
            Un especialista es un médico con formación avanzada en un área específica, capacitado para diagnosticar y tratar enfermedades complejas de forma más precisa.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 group cursor-pointer marker:content-[''] border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-[#00a3e0] transition-all overflow-hidden bg-white/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          <summary class="text-xl font-bold text-[#004b87] flex justify-between items-center outline-none list-none marker:content-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            ¿Cómo elegir la especialidad médica correcta?
            <i class="ph ph-caret-down transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-[#00a3e0] text-2xl"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 pr-8">
            Depende de tus síntomas. Por ejemplo, problemas digestivos corresponden a gastroenterología, síntomas respiratorios a neumología y afecciones de la piel a dermatología.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 group cursor-pointer marker:content-[''] border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-[#00a3e0] transition-all overflow-hidden bg-white/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          <summary class="text-xl font-bold text-[#004b87] flex justify-between items-center outline-none list-none marker:content-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            ¿Qué estudios debo llevar a mi primera consulta?
            <i class="ph ph-caret-down transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-[#00a3e0] text-2xl"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 pr-8">
            Se recomienda llevar estudios previos, análisis clínicos, radiografías o cualquier historial médico que ayude al especialista a evaluar tu caso de forma más completa.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 group cursor-pointer marker:content-[''] border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-[#00a3e0] transition-all overflow-hidden bg-white/60 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md">
          <summary class="text-xl font-bold text-[#004b87] flex justify-between items-center outline-none list-none marker:content-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
            ¿Necesito referencia médica para consultar a un especialista?
            <i class="ph ph-caret-down transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform text-[#00a3e0] text-2xl"></i>
          </summary>
          <div class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-100 pt-4 pr-8">
            No es necesario. Puedes agendar directamente con el especialista indicado según tus síntomas o necesidades.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Lógica de Animaciones GSAP y Load More -->
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      
      // Load More Logic
      const loadMoreBtn = document.getElementById('loadMoreBtn');
      const dataNode = document.getElementById('remainingSpecData');
      const listContainer = document.getElementById('specialtiesList');
      const loadMoreContainer = document.getElementById('loadMoreContainer');
      
      function getIcon(name) {
        const n = name.toLowerCase();
        let icon = "ph-stethoscope";
        if (n.includes('cardio')) icon = "ph-heartbeat";
        else if (n.includes('gastro')) icon = "ph-first-aid";
        else if (n.includes('pediat')) icon = "ph-baby";
        else if (n.includes('ortop') || n.includes('traum')) icon = "ph-activity";
        else if (n.includes('neuro')) icon = "ph-brain";
        else if (n.includes('derm')) icon = "ph-hand";
        else if (n.includes('neumo')) icon = "ph-wind";
        else if (n.includes('psiq') || n.includes('psic')) icon = "ph-brain";
        else if (n.includes('hepa')) icon = "ph-drop";
        else if (n.includes('hema')) icon = "ph-drop";
        else if (n.includes('gine') || n.includes('obste')) icon = "ph-baby";
        else if (n.includes('uro')) icon = "ph-drop";
        else if (n.includes('cirug')) icon = "ph-scissors";
        else if (n.includes('onco') || n.includes('cancer')) icon = "ph-dna";
        else if (n.includes('alergi') || n.includes('inmun')) icon = "ph-plant";
        else if (n.includes('bariat')) icon = "ph-person";
        else if (n.includes('electro')) icon = "ph-activity";
        else if (n.includes('endo')) icon = "ph-drop";
        else if (n.includes('geri')) icon = "ph-users";
        else if (n.includes('infec')) icon = "ph-shield-plus";
        return icon;
      }

      function slugify(text) {
        if (!text) return '';
        return text.toString().toLowerCase().trim()
          .normalize('NFD')
          .replace(/[\u0300-\u036f]/g, '')
          .replace(/\s+/g, '-')
          .replace(/[^\w\-]+/g, '')
          .replace(/\-\-+/g, '-');
      }

      if (loadMoreBtn && dataNode && listContainer) {
        loadMoreBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
          let remainingSpecialties = JSON.parse(dataNode.textContent);
          
          const nextBatch = remainingSpecialties.splice(0, 9);
          dataNode.textContent = JSON.stringify(remainingSpecialties);
          
          let newHtml = '';
          nextBatch.forEach(spec => {
            const icon = getIcon(spec.nombre);
            newHtml += `
              <li class="specialty-card new-added-card h-full group relative bg-white p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:border-sky-200 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col items-start translate-y-0 hover:-translate-y-2">
                 <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-sky-600 mb-6 group-hover:bg-sky-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
                   <i class="ph ${icon} text-3xl"></i>
                 </div>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors uppercase leading-tight">${spec.nombre}</h3>
                 <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
                   Atención médica especializada de primer nivel, orientada al diagnóstico y tratamiento preciso.
                 </p>
                 <div class="mt-auto pt-4 w-full">
                   <a href="/especialidades/${slugify(spec.nombre)}" class="text-sky-600 font-semibold text-sm flex items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                     Ver más <i class="ph ph-arrow-right ml-1"></i>
                   </a>
                 </div>
              </li>
            `;
          });
          
          listContainer.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', newHtml);
          
          if (remainingSpecialties.length === 0) {
            loadMoreContainer.style.display = 'none';
          }
          
          if (typeof window.gsap !== "undefined" && window.ScrollTrigger) {
            window.gsap.from(".new-added-card", {
              y: 40,
              opacity: 0,
              duration: 0.6,
              stagger: 0.1,
              ease: "power2.out",
              clearProps: "all",
              onComplete: () => {
                document.querySelectorAll('.new-added-card').forEach(el => el.classList.remove('new-added-card'));
                window.ScrollTrigger.refresh();
              }
            });
          }
        });
      }

      // Small timeout to ensure custom elements/images loads visually stabilize
      setTimeout(() => {
          if (typeof window.gsap !== "undefined" && window.ScrollTrigger) {
            
            // Animación de las cards de especialidad (Stagger)
            window.gsap.from(".specialty-card:not(.new-added-card)", {
              scrollTrigger: {
                trigger: ".specialties-section",
                start: "top 80%",
              },
              y: 40,
              opacity: 0,
              duration: 0.8,
              stagger: 0.15,
              ease: "power2.out",
              clearProps: "all",
            });

            // Animación de la línea de proceso
            window.gsap.from(".process-step", {
              scrollTrigger: {
                trigger: ".process-section",
                start: "top 75%",
              },
              scale: 0.8,
              opacity: 0,
              y: 30,
              duration: 0.6,
              stagger: 0.2,
              ease: "back.out(1.5)",
              clearProps: "all",
            });
          }
      }, 100);
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
